---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Modern Work &mdash; Forge T Labs"
  description="Microsoft 365 and Modern Work services from Forge T Labs."
  canonical=""
  ogType="website"
  active="Services"
>
<main id="top">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <a href="/services">Services</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Modern Work</div>
    <h1><em>Modern Work</em> on Microsoft 365.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Secure, productive workplaces your people actually want to use. We deploy, secure and drive adoption of Microsoft 365 &mdash; from tenant setup to Teams, SharePoint and endpoint management.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">What we deliver</span>
      <h2>A modern workplace, <em>secured and adopted</em>.</h2>
      <p>Rolling out Microsoft 365 is the easy part &mdash; doing it securely, and getting people to actually use it, is where we focus.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-cap">
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M7 18a4 4 0 0 1 0-8 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 10.6-1.5A3.8 3.8 0 0 1 18 18H7Z"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Tenant setup &amp; migration</h4>
        <p>Provisioning, plus email and content migration from legacy platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="4" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="15" y="14" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><path d="M9 7h6a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v4" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Teams &amp; Teams Phone</h4>
        <p>Collaboration and cloud calling, designed and rolled out properly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg></div>
        <h4>SharePoint &amp; intranet</h4>
        <p>Modern SharePoint sites and intranets with real governance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3l8 3v6c0 5-3.5 8-8 9-4.5-1-8-4-8-9V6l8-3Z" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Security hardening</h4>
        <p>Conditional access, MFA, DLP and security baselines across the tenant.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.2"/><path d="M12 2v3m0 14v3M2 12h3m14 0h3M5 5l2 2m10 10l2 2M5 19l2-2M17 7l2-2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Intune &amp; endpoints</h4>
        <p>Device enrolment, compliance and application management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 20s-7-4.5-7-10a4 4 0 0 1 7-2.5A4 4 0 0 1 19 10c0 5.5-7 10-7 10Z"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Adoption &amp; change</h4>
        <p>Structured programmes that drive real end-user engagement.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:44px">
      <span class="mono">Use cases</span>
      <h2>Where this <em>delivers</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-split">
      <div class="svc-list reveal">
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">01</span>
          <div><h4>Migrating off legacy email</h4><p>Move mailboxes, files and content into Microsoft 365 with minimal disruption.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">02</span>
          <div><h4>Securing the tenant</h4><p>Apply conditional access, MFA and DLP to close gaps in a Microsoft 365 estate.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">03</span>
          <div><h4>Rolling out Teams Phone</h4><p>Replace legacy phone systems with cloud calling in Teams.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">04</span>
          <div><h4>Building a modern intranet</h4><p>Give staff a SharePoint intranet that is actually used, not abandoned.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">05</span>
          <div><h4>Managing devices with Intune</h4><p>Bring laptops and mobiles under compliance and application management.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-aside reveal">
        <h4>Industry spotlight</h4>
        <p class="lead-sm">Modern Work is industry-agnostic &mdash; these sectors feel the benefit fastest.</p>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Healthcare &amp; life sciences</div>
          <div class="d">Secure, compliant collaboration for clinical and back-office teams.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Financial services</div>
          <div class="d">Microsoft 365 with the governance and controls regulators expect.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Education</div>
          <div class="d">Identity, devices and collaboration for staff and students at scale.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band reveal">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <h2>Modern Work on Microsoft 365. &mdash; let's talk.</h2>
      <p>Tell us where you are today and what you are trying to reach. We will map a practical
        path on the Microsoft Cloud.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Start a project &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/services">All services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
